(1) Three members from the House Committee on Commerce appointed by the
speaker of the House of Representatives.
(2) Three members from the House Committee on Ways and Means appointed by
the speaker of the House of Representatives.
(3) One state representative from the Northshore Legislative Delegation appointed
by the speaker of the House of Representatives.
BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the state representative from the Northshore
Legislative Delegation shall serve as chair of the select committee.
BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the speaker of the House of Representatives
shall designate staff to assist the committee in its work.
BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the select committee shall submit a report of its
findings and recommendations to the members of the House of Representatives of the
Legislature of Louisiana and the David R. Poynter Legislative Research Library no later than
thirty days prior to the convening of the 2027 Regular Session.
BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that legislative authority for the select committee
shall terminate upon the convening of the 2027 Regular Session.
